flowRoot.flowPara: Ditto, but with Monitors/Webcams facing inwards

I control the robot on the left, using "Fingers", which broadcasts a 360 degree video stream of my head, including audio out through speakers (me speaking). The webcams on the robot also give me a 360 degree view of the robot's position, and also has audio in through microphone (people/aliens speaking).
